OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,FThe Ministry of Defence has confirmed
OL,8,Fthat it will not provide financial
OL,9,Fsupport for people whose homes were
OL,10,Fdamaged by the .
OL,12,FA number of homes and gardens on St
OL,13,FMichael Avenue in were damaged during
OL,14,Fthe successful removal of the Second
OL,15,FWorld War bomb in February.
OL,17,FIn a press release, the local MP Luke
OL,18,FPollard said he was seeking an urgent
OL,19,Fmeeting with ministers.
