OL,7,FAfter the bomb disposal, he spoke with
OL,8,FDefence Minister Dr Andrew Murrison MP
OL,9,Fto ask if the MOD had a policy of
OL,10,Fproviding support for the repair of
OL,11,Fhousing and gardens damaged during
OL,12,Fbomb disposal operations like that
OL,13,Fcarried out in Keyham.
OL,15,FMr Pollard said that Dr Murrison had
OL,16,Fsuggested that there may be a route
OL,17,Ffor assistance in such circumstances
OL,18,Fand undertook to investigate.
