OL,7,FHowever, according to the MP, he has
OL,8,Fnow said in a letter that the MOD
OL,9,F"does not consider itself liable" for
OL,10,Fthe damage.
OL,12,FDr Murrison is said to have cited the
OL,13,Flegal precedent of the Exeter bomb and
OL,14,Fadded that residents should instead
OL,15,F"arrive at a solution" with their home
OL,16,Finsurance companies.
