OL,7,FMr Pollard said that it has been
OL,8,F"frustrating" to have received
OL,9,Fcontradictory advice from the Minister
OL,10,Fwhen residents "just want their lives
OL,11,Fback to normal as soon as possible".
OL,13,FThe MP has replied to Dr Murrison to
OL,14,Frequest an urgent meeting to clarify
OL,15,Fwhat government help and guidance is
OL,16,Favailable to affected families under
OL,17,FMOD policy.
