OL,7,FMr Pollard says he has also written to
OL,8,Finsurance companies to push for
OL,9,Fcomprehensive support for those
OL,10,Faffected, as well as working with
OL,11,FPlymouth City Council.
OL,13,FPlymouth City Council has offered
OL,14,Fresidents support such as deep
OL,15,Fcleaning and repairs.
OL,17,FThe MP has also argued that insurance
OL,18,Fcompanies should not use an "act of
OL,19,Fwar" loophole in insurance policies.
