OL,7,FBuilding Plymouth, a Plymouth City
OL,8,FCouncil-led partnership with the
OL,9,Fconstruction industry, has pledged
OL,10,Fhelp with repairs for a damaged back
OL,11,Fwall, garden repairs, and decking.
OL,13,FLuke Pollard MP, Member of Parliament
OL,14,Ffor Plymouth Sutton and Devonport,
OL,15,Fsaid: "It is frustrating to get
OL,16,Fcontradictory advice from the
OL,17,Fgovernment. Residents just want to get
OL,18,Ftheir lives back to normal as soon as
OL,19,Fpossible.
