OL,7,F"The Army and Royal Navy stepped up to
OL,8,Fhelp Keyham when we needed them,
OL,9,Fshowing extraordinary skill, bravery
OL,10,Fand expertise to safely remove the
OL,11,Fbomb.
OL,13,F"It makes it so very disappointing
OL,14,Fthat the government has been slow and
OL,15,Fconfused in the recovery phase. It
OL,16,Fwould be unacceptable for residents to
OL,17,Fbe left worse off. I will keep working
OL,18,Fto prevent that."
